like MICR.

2713
02:01:09,840 --> 02:01:10,829
It's some kind of a...

2714
02:01:10,880 --> 02:01:12,552
you know,
some kind of a drafting ink.

2715
02:01:12,600 --> 02:01:14,750
You know, the kind you get
at a stationery store.

2716
02:01:14,800 --> 02:01:16,074
