2722
02:01:28,120 --> 02:01:29,075
I already got a job here.

2723
02:01:29,120 --> 02:01:30,519
You know, l, uh,
deliver the mail.

2724
02:01:32,560 --> 02:01:37,076
Frank, we have the power
to take you out of prison.

2725
02:01:37,120 --> 02:01:38,712
You'd be placed
in the custody of the FBI

2726
02:01:38,760 --> 02:01:40,796
where you'd serve out
the remainder of your sentence

2727
02:01:40,840 --> 02:01:42,478
as an employee
of the federal government.

2728
02:01:45,040 --> 02:01:47,031
Under whose custody?

2729
02:01:52,920 --> 02:01:55,354
<i>(phone ringing)</i>

2730
02:01:55,400 --> 02:01:57,960
Hi. L-I'm Frank Abagnale.

2731
02:01:58,000 --> 02:02:00,355
I'm supposed to start work
here today.

2732
02:02:00,400 --> 02:02:02,868
It's a tour company
operating out of the BVI.

2733
02:02:02,920 --> 02:02:05,036
