<i>Good morning. </i>

2821
02:07:30,280 --> 02:07:32,236
I've, uh, called this meeting
to discuss

2822
02:07:32,280 --> 02:07:34,475
a new type of check fraud
and counterfeiting

2823
02:07:34,520 --> 02:07:36,829
which the unsub is washing
and altering checks

2824
02:07:36,880 --> 02:07:38,757
then passing them
throughout Arizona.

2825
02:07:38,800 --> 02:07:42,759
<i>(panting)</i>

2826
02:07:42,800 --> 02:07:44,279
This unsub is a big dog

2827
