Sorry.

2831
02:07:57,920 --> 02:08:01,196
We have a recovered check
on Agent Reiter's desk.

2832
02:08:01,240 --> 02:08:03,151
Why don't we step out
to the bullpen?

2833
02:08:07,320 --> 02:08:11,074
There's impressions
on every line.

2834
02:08:11,120 --> 02:08:14,715
Looks like the original amount
was for $60.

2835
02:08:18,280 --> 02:08:19,474
Mind if I take a look?

2836
02:08:22,840 --> 02:08:25,718
