2837
02:08:27,480 --> 02:08:30,278
Cost the bank $16,000.

2838
02:08:30,320 --> 02:08:32,197
It's a real check.

2839
02:08:32,240 --> 02:08:34,151
Yeah.

2840
02:08:34,200 --> 02:08:35,349
Yeah. It's been washed.

2841
02:08:35,400 --> 02:08:37,277
The only thing original
is the signature.

2842
02:08:37,320 --> 02:08:39,072
But it's perfect, Carl.
I mean...

2843
02:08:39,120 --> 02:08:41,315
I mean, this isn't hydrochloride
or bleach.

2844
02:08:41,360 --> 02:08:43,555
No.

2845
02:08:43,600 --> 02:08:45,238
Something new.

2846
02:08:45,280 --> 02:08:47,236
Maybe a nail polish remover
where the acetone

2847
02:08:47,280 --> 02:08:49,157
removes the ink
that's not been printed?

2848
02:08:53,040 --> 02:08:55,873
How did you do it, Frank?

2849
02:08:55,920 --> 02:08:58,798
How did you cheat
on the bar exam in Louisiana?

2850
02:09:04,000 --> 02:09:07,072
I didn't cheat.

2851
02:09:07,120 --> 02:09:10,590
I studied for two weeks
and I passed.

2852
02:09:11,640 --> 02:09:13,835
Is that the truth, Frank?

2853
02:09:13,880 --> 02:09:16,030
Is that the truth?

2854
02:09:16,080 --> 02:09:18,469
I'll bet this guy steals checks
out of mailboxes.

2855
02:09:18,520 --> 02:09:20,954
He washes off their names
and he puts on his own.

2856
02:09:22,720 --> 02:09:24,870
You're saying that he's a local?

2857
02:09:24,920 --> 02:09:26,148
Well, if it were me, you know

2858
02:09:26,200 --> 02:09:28,395
I'd call the bank first,
I'd check out the balance...

2859
02:09:28,440 --> 02:09:29,998
Make sure there's enough money
in there

2860
02:09:30,040 --> 02:09:31,189
to make it worth your while.

2861
02:09:31,240 --> 02:09:32,309
Exactly.

2862
02:09:32,360 --> 02:09:34,271
You know, Carl, I think
this guy's pretty smart.

2863
02:09:34,320 --> 02:09:35,878
I guess all we have to do now
is catch him.

2864
02:09:35,920 --> 02:09:37,353
We'll start first thing
in the morning.

